title: mojo script progress
content:
#N/A / N/A / Evo. - Petal Blizzard
#N/A / N/A / 1 - Power Whip
#1 - Tackle
#1 - Growl
#5 - Vine Whip
#8 - Leech Seed
#11 - Poison Powder
#11 - Sleep Powder
#14 - Take Down
#17 / 19 - Razor Leaf
#20 / 22 - Sweet Scent
#23 / 25 - Double-Edge
#26 / 28 - Worry Seed
#29 / 31 - Seed Bomb
#32 / 34 - Synthesis
#35 / 37 / 42 - Petal Dance
#38 / 40 / 48 - Solar Beam


import pprint
import sys

highestEvo = 1
file = open(sys.argv[1], "r")
for line in file:
    line = line.replace("N/A", "NA")
    arr = line.split("/")
    if (len(arr) > highestEvo):
        highestEvo = len(arr)
file.seek(0, 0)

moves = {}
moveIndex = {}
for i in range(0, highestEvo):
    moves[i] = {}
    moveIndex[i] = 0

for line in file:
    print(line)
    line = line.replace("N/A", "NA")
    arr = line.split("/")
    arrBkp = arr
    if len(arr) != highestEvo:
        for i in range(len(arr), highestEvo):
            arr[i] = arrBkp[-1]
    #for i in range(0, len(arr)):
    for j in range(0, highestEvo):
        if ("NA" not in arr[j]):
            moves[j][moveIndex[j]] = "MOVE_" + line.strip().split(" - ")[1].upper().replace(" ", "_").replace("-", "_")
            moveIndex[j] = moveIndex[j] + 1

print(highestEvo)
pprint.pp(moves)
